==古病理学==
2001年，Bruce Rothschild和其他人发布了[[兽脚类|兽脚类]]及其习性影响的[[疲劳性骨折|疲劳性骨折]]和肌腱撕脱研究检测证据。他们发现17个纤手龙脚骨中有一个患有疲劳性骨折。<ref name="rothschild-dino">Rothschild, B., Tanke, D. H., and Ford, T. L., 2001, Theropod stress fractures and tendon avulsions as a clue to activity: In: Mesozoic Vertebrate Life, edited by Tanke, D. H., and Carpenter, K., Indiana University Press, p. 331-336.</ref>

